♪Time surges into summer♪

12
00:01:05,140 --> 00:01:08,430
♪The firmament resonates for me♪

13
00:01:08,700 --> 00:01:12,350
♪Igniting hearts, and flames of the heart♪

14
00:01:12,520 --> 00:01:16,020
♪Dedication, determined dedication♪

15
00:01:16,170 --> 00:01:18,980
♪Heaven and earth, life and death,
we'll be together♪

16
00:01:18,980 --> 00:01:23,550
♪That's a promise that will not waver♪

17
00:01:23,550 --> 00:01:26,980
=Battle Through The Heaven=

18
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:29,980
=Episode 7=

19
00:01:36,780 --> 00:01:39,100
That year, I asked you
to kill Yao Chen with poison.

20
00:01:39,290 --> 00:01:40,570
To join the Hall of Souls,

21
00:01:40,570 --> 00:01:42,330
you did that without hesitation.

22
00:01:44,460 --> 00:01:46,930
Now, you want to kill him again.

23
00:01:51,100 --> 00:01:51,940
Han Feng,

24
00:01:53,650 --> 00:01:54,820
do you not care

25
00:01:54,820 --> 00:01:57,140
even a little bit about your master?

26
00:01:57,330 --> 00:01:59,370
Since I pledged loyalty to you,

27
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:00,900
I've cared about no one else.

28
00:02:02,100 --> 00:02:02,940
Besides,

29
00:02:05,140 --> 00:02:06,010
Yao Chen...

30
00:02:07,180 --> 00:02:08,610
He disappointed me again.

31
00:02:09,660 --> 00:02:12,860
He passed on Flame Mantra to Xiao Yan!

32
00:02:14,690 --> 00:02:16,170
I shouldn't have trusted him.

33
00:02:18,420 --> 00:02:19,890
Give me an order

34
00:02:21,220 --> 00:02:23,530
and I will kill Yao Chen again

35
00:02:24,380 --> 00:02:25,500
to tie up loose ends.

36
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:29,250
What is your plan?

37
00:02:32,860 --> 00:02:34,170
I've figured it out.

38
00:02:35,860 --> 00:02:36,940
Xiao Yan's father

39
00:02:37,660 --> 00:02:39,330
is imprisoned in the Misty Cloud Sect.

40
00:02:41,530 --> 00:02:44,060
He went to Jia Nan Academy

41
00:02:44,580 --> 00:02:46,060
just to save his father.

42
00:02:47,580 --> 00:02:50,090
Chief Yun Shan of the Misty Cloud Sect

43
00:02:51,090 --> 00:02:52,730
has been having closed-door cultivation.

44
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:55,140
Elder,

45
00:02:55,810 --> 00:02:57,730
if you give him a little help

46
00:02:57,860 --> 00:02:59,250
and do him a favor,

47
00:03:00,530 --> 00:03:04,500
I believe he'll be under our control.

48
00:03:06,140 --> 00:03:06,980
By then,

49
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:10,220
we can lure Xiao Yan
to the Misty Cloud Sect

50
00:03:11,730 --> 00:03:13,060
and force Yao Chen to show up.

51
00:03:15,170 --> 00:03:16,380
Then you will get

52
00:03:17,220 --> 00:03:19,530
the Bone Spirit Cold Flame.

53
00:03:24,060 --> 00:03:26,020
It's far more powerful

54
00:03:26,530 --> 00:03:28,610
than the Fallen Heart Flame.

55
00:03:32,810 --> 00:03:33,810
Then go for it.

56
00:03:34,530 --> 00:03:36,170
Don't let anything go wrong again.

57
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:38,020
Otherwise,

58
00:03:38,690 --> 00:03:40,890
you'd be of no use.

59
00:04:03,300 --> 00:04:04,890
Mr. Yao is still very weak.

60
00:04:11,330 --> 00:04:12,170
Flame Poison

61
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:15,090
has been the most difficult poison.

62
00:04:15,970 --> 00:04:18,170
Because it's stuck in the veins.

63
00:04:19,010 --> 00:04:21,660
Do you know the best antidote for it?

64
00:04:26,260 --> 00:04:27,410
Spiritual Recovery Purple Pill?

65
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:34,300
(Elders' House)

66
00:04:44,540 --> 00:04:45,380
Headmaster.

67
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:48,340
Xiao Yan?

68
00:04:49,780 --> 00:04:51,170
How are you recovering?

69
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:52,940
I'm fine now.

70
00:04:54,170 --> 00:04:56,450
I have to discuss something with you.

71
00:04:57,610 --> 00:05:00,060
The Fallen Heart Flame?

72
00:05:03,730 --> 00:05:04,570
Yes.

73
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:06,500
I conquered it.

74
00:05:08,380 --> 00:05:09,220
So,

75
00:05:09,450 --> 00:05:10,820
on the day you entered our academy,

76
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:12,220
you clamored for entry to the ranking

77
00:05:13,330 --> 00:05:15,820
just to get into the Tower

78
00:05:15,820 --> 00:05:17,100
and conquer the flame, huh?

79
00:05:21,570 --> 00:05:22,410
Forgive me, Headmaster.

80
00:05:24,010 --> 00:05:25,010
I did come to this academy

81
00:05:25,290 --> 00:05:26,780
to conquer the Fallen Heart Flame.

82
00:05:27,500 --> 00:05:28,340
I didn't mean

83
00:05:28,730 --> 00:05:30,010
to keep it from you.

84
00:05:31,850 --> 00:05:33,840
Heavenly Flames were born
between heaven and earth

85
00:05:34,170 --> 00:05:35,100
and they were ownerless.

86
00:05:36,260 --> 00:05:38,060
What harm is there when you borrow it?

87
00:05:40,010 --> 00:05:40,850
Thank you, Headmaster.

88
00:05:42,980 --> 00:05:44,820
How's Mr. Yao now?

89
00:05:47,010 --> 00:05:48,100
He's still in the Storage Ring.

90
00:05:48,380 --> 00:05:49,220
He's not dying.

91
00:05:49,570 --> 00:05:50,410
But

92
00:05:50,730 --> 00:05:52,700
he's badly injured and still in a coma.

93
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:55,450
If you need any pills, let me know.

94
00:05:55,820 --> 00:05:56,730
I've checked it.

95
00:05:56,890 --> 00:05:59,290
Only the Spiritual Recovery Purple Pill
can heal Mr. Yao.

96
00:06:02,130 --> 00:06:04,940
I'm afraid such a high-grade pill

97
00:06:05,940 --> 00:06:07,220
is only available in the Central Plains.

98
00:06:08,170 --> 00:06:10,130
I'm sure Han Feng has some.

99
00:06:11,660 --> 00:06:12,500
Han Feng?

100
00:06:13,410 --> 00:06:14,500
When I fought Han Feng that day,

101
00:06:14,890 --> 00:06:16,130
he also suffered from Flame Poison.

102
00:06:16,820 --> 00:06:18,060
Nearly as badly as Mr. Yao.

103
00:06:18,330 --> 00:06:20,060
So, he needs such pills for recovery.

104
00:06:22,290 --> 00:06:24,260
It makes sense.

105
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:27,820
Han Feng's lair
is in the Blackhorn Domain.

106
00:06:28,330 --> 00:06:30,330
If you really want to go there,

107
00:06:31,380 --> 00:06:32,820
I do have a favor to ask.

108
00:06:33,940 --> 00:06:34,780
Go ahead, Headmaster.

109
00:06:37,060 --> 00:06:38,330
When the Tower was unsealed,

110
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:40,220
Bai Shan was gone.

111
00:06:40,940 --> 00:06:43,450
I guess Han Feng abducted him.

112
00:06:44,780 --> 00:06:47,570
He was misguided
and betrayed our academy.

113
00:06:48,820 --> 00:06:50,890
But he's still one of our disciples.

114
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:53,410
We should rescue him.

115
00:06:54,330 --> 00:06:55,170
Headmaster,

116
00:06:55,890 --> 00:06:58,570
Bai Shan hated our academy because of me.

117
00:06:59,330 --> 00:07:00,700
I'm somewhat involved.

118
00:07:02,170 --> 00:07:04,540
So, I will take him back.

119
00:07:12,220 --> 00:07:14,130
Why are you following us?

120
00:07:15,610 --> 00:07:17,940
It is my duty to protect Miss Xun'er.

121
00:07:18,410 --> 00:07:19,540
Hope you'll get used to that.

122
00:07:21,170 --> 00:07:23,380
I'm used to that, of course.

123
00:07:24,330 --> 00:07:26,220
Exploring the Hall of Souls
is also my duty.

124
00:07:26,330 --> 00:07:27,450
Hope you'll be aware.

125
00:07:28,380 --> 00:07:29,220
I'm aware.

126
00:07:29,850 --> 00:07:31,890
But on this mission, I call the shots.

127
00:07:31,940 --> 00:07:33,060
You have to listen to me.

128
00:07:33,540 --> 00:07:34,450
I also hope

129
00:07:35,170 --> 00:07:37,130
you can get used to that and be aware.

130
00:07:39,610 --> 00:07:40,450
Miss.

131
00:07:42,170 --> 00:07:43,010
I'm worried

132
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:44,700
that Xiao Yan isn't sure

133
00:07:45,380 --> 00:07:46,450
about the location of Feng City.

134
00:07:47,540 --> 00:07:48,380
Maybe...

135
00:07:49,850 --> 00:07:50,980
I trust Xiao Yan.

136
00:07:51,820 --> 00:07:52,660
Xun'er,

137
00:07:52,730 --> 00:07:53,570
catch up.

138
00:07:54,010 --> 00:07:54,850
Coming.

139
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:18,940
What?

140
00:08:20,130 --> 00:08:22,100
Stop when you can't find the way?

141
00:08:25,980 --> 00:08:26,820
Here, Xun'er.

142
00:08:30,940 --> 00:08:31,780
Here.

143
00:08:35,140 --> 00:08:36,260
How long has that fight

144
00:08:37,310 --> 00:08:38,180
been over?

145
00:08:38,210 --> 00:08:39,050
For four days.

146
00:08:39,060 --> 00:08:40,820
Four days and three nights, precisely.

147
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:43,740
We should wait, then.

148
00:08:44,530 --> 00:08:45,370
Until when?

149
00:08:46,820 --> 00:08:49,730
Until Han Feng finishes making
the Spiritual Recovery Purple Pill.

150
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:53,290
This pill has a special efficacy

151
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:55,290
and can't be preserved for a long time.

152
00:08:56,140 --> 00:08:57,340
Han Feng is badly injured.

153
00:08:58,260 --> 00:08:59,290
He has to make it immediately

154
00:08:59,730 --> 00:09:01,940
And he must take it
as soon as it's finished.

155
00:09:02,460 --> 00:09:04,290
It takes four days and nights
to make such a pill.

156
00:09:04,620 --> 00:09:05,480
When it's done,

157
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:07,500
there will be strong energy fluctuations.

158
00:09:07,970 --> 00:09:09,340
So, you knew from the beginning

159
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:10,920
that when we arrive
in the Blackhorn Domain,

160
00:09:11,060 --> 00:09:12,090
we can know where Feng City is

161
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:14,290
according to energy fluctuations.

162
00:09:17,460 --> 00:09:18,460
There's still some time.

163
00:09:19,260 --> 00:09:20,100
Don't push yourself.

164
00:09:21,170 --> 00:09:22,010
Let's go.

165
00:09:40,170 --> 00:09:41,210
The pill is almost done.

166
00:09:41,700 --> 00:09:42,540
Hurry.

167
00:09:50,700 --> 00:09:51,540
I said,

168
00:09:51,970 --> 00:09:52,810
leave me alone!

169
00:09:59,210 --> 00:10:01,700
Xiao Yan conquered
the Fallen Heart Flame?

170
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:10,610
Yao Chen got out of the Storage Ring

171
00:10:11,900 --> 00:10:13,500
and he didn't regain his Dou Qi.

172
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:16,300
They

173
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:20,260
must be here for my pill.

174
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:23,580
Sadly,

175
00:10:24,410 --> 00:10:25,730
I haven't fully recovered.

176
00:10:27,290 --> 00:10:28,530
If I forcibly

177
00:10:29,970 --> 00:10:31,410
stop making it,

178
00:10:32,460 --> 00:10:34,210
my old injury will relapse.

179
00:10:37,060 --> 00:10:37,900
Instead of

180
00:10:39,380 --> 00:10:41,290
giving the pill to someone else,

181
00:10:45,530 --> 00:10:46,500
I would rather...

182
00:10:49,530 --> 00:10:50,370
Go.

183
00:10:51,170 --> 00:10:52,850
Go get Bai Shan to me.

184
00:11:06,610 --> 00:11:08,850
The smell of the pill came from ahead.

185
00:11:09,970 --> 00:11:10,810
Let's go.

186
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:18,300
Bai Shan!

187
00:11:19,770 --> 00:11:20,610
Stay back.

188
00:11:27,820 --> 00:11:29,380
Here's the Spiritual Recovery Purple Pill.

189
00:11:31,700 --> 00:11:32,540
Xiao Yan,

190
00:11:33,730 --> 00:11:34,820
you come over alone.

191
00:11:35,340 --> 00:11:36,180
Wait.

192
00:11:37,650 --> 00:11:39,380
Han Feng set the formation, I assume.

193
00:11:40,140 --> 00:11:41,610
Bai Shan is standing in the center.

194
00:11:41,610 --> 00:11:42,460
This is a trap.

195
00:11:44,530 --> 00:11:45,940
I have to go, anyway.

196
00:11:47,730 --> 00:11:49,090
Later, I'll throw the pill out.

197
00:11:49,900 --> 00:11:50,740
You have to catch it.

198
00:11:54,210 --> 00:11:55,050
Bai Shan,

199
00:11:55,350 --> 00:11:56,200
here I am.

200
00:11:56,210 --> 00:11:57,460
The rest of you, freeze!

201
00:11:59,730 --> 00:12:00,570
Bai Shan,

202
00:12:01,730 --> 00:12:02,820
I know you hate me.

203
00:12:04,170 --> 00:12:05,820
But Xun'er was your friend.

204
00:12:07,060 --> 00:12:08,530
If you still have a conscience,

205
00:12:09,290 --> 00:12:10,130
don't hurt her.

206
00:12:10,140 --> 00:12:10,980
Shut up!

207
00:12:11,460 --> 00:12:12,340
You don't get to lecture me.

208
00:12:15,170 --> 00:12:16,010
Xun'er,

209
00:12:17,970 --> 00:12:18,810
back off.

210
00:12:19,260 --> 00:12:20,970
Listen to him. Don't follow me.

211
00:12:30,020 --> 00:12:30,860
Bai Shan,

212
00:12:31,580 --> 00:12:32,800
go back to the Academy with me.

213
00:12:33,850 --> 00:12:34,770
Elder Su Qian

214
00:12:35,530 --> 00:12:37,210
will give you a fair punishment.

215
00:12:40,060 --> 00:12:40,900
No.

216
00:12:44,060 --> 00:12:45,020
I'm not going back.

217
00:12:47,610 --> 00:12:49,340
I can never go back there.

218
00:12:53,650 --> 00:12:55,290
I know you hate me
for badly injuring you.

219
00:12:56,460 --> 00:12:57,940
But it's not that you can't get back

220
00:12:57,940 --> 00:12:59,090
what you lost.

221
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:01,850
Mr. Yao is the best alchemist

222
00:13:01,850 --> 00:13:02,900
on Dou Qi Continent.

223
00:13:03,340 --> 00:13:04,610
He can help you regain Dou Qi.

224
00:13:08,700 --> 00:13:09,580
You're going to help me?

225
00:13:13,060 --> 00:13:14,530
You destroyed my Dou Qi

226
00:13:14,530 --> 00:13:16,410
and ruined everything I had!

227
00:13:18,410 --> 00:13:19,580
And now, you stand here,

228
00:13:19,580 --> 00:13:22,140
proudly saying you want to help me.

229
00:13:25,730 --> 00:13:27,290
You make me sick.

230
00:13:29,730 --> 00:13:30,970
So sick!

231
00:13:33,380 --> 00:13:34,220
I know.

232
00:13:35,260 --> 00:13:36,460
Without me,

233
00:13:38,260 --> 00:13:39,610
you would be on the ranking.

234
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:40,840
You would be the first disciple

235
00:13:40,850 --> 00:13:42,340
to enter Blazing Sky Qi Refining Tower.

236
00:13:43,090 --> 00:13:43,940
But trust me.

237
00:13:43,940 --> 00:13:45,460
I never meant to fight with you for this!

238
00:13:51,530 --> 00:13:52,700
You know what, Xiao Yan?

239
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:57,500
This is what I hate you most.

240
00:14:00,020 --> 00:14:01,410
You never cared about what you got

241
00:14:01,410 --> 00:14:03,380
at Jia Nan Academy.

242
00:14:05,530 --> 00:14:07,530
You easily got everything

243
00:14:08,460 --> 00:14:10,290
and then abandoned it quickly.

244
00:14:13,940 --> 00:14:15,380
You'll never understand.

245
00:14:18,340 --> 00:14:20,210
What you didn't care about

246
00:14:22,140 --> 00:14:24,140
and what you carelessly abandoned,

247
00:14:26,170 --> 00:14:28,140
they were supposed to be mine!

248
00:14:29,380 --> 00:14:30,850
They should belong to me!

249
00:14:32,210 --> 00:14:33,700
You lost your Dou Qi, so what?

250
00:14:36,020 --> 00:14:37,580
You've been talented since you were born.

251
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:43,290
For such little frustrations,
you just gave up.

252
00:14:46,140 --> 00:14:46,980
I...

253
00:14:49,850 --> 00:14:51,380
When I was 13,

254
00:14:52,940 --> 00:14:53,970
I lost all my Dou Qi

255
00:14:56,090 --> 00:14:57,410
and became a joke.

256
00:14:58,020 --> 00:14:59,020
But I wasn't convinced.

257
00:14:59,770 --> 00:15:00,700
I didn't give in.

258
00:15:01,850 --> 00:15:03,140
I've come this far

259
00:15:03,140 --> 00:15:05,260
after I was broken
and started all over again.

260
00:15:05,940 --> 00:15:06,780
Bai Shan,

261
00:15:07,970 --> 00:15:09,060
you can also do that.

262
00:15:17,530 --> 00:15:18,370
Bai Shan.

263
00:15:20,850 --> 00:15:22,290
If you're still a proud man,

264
00:15:23,170 --> 00:15:24,170
go back with me.

265
00:15:25,820 --> 00:15:27,210
When you regain your Dou Qi,

266
00:15:28,460 --> 00:15:30,460
we'll have a fair competition.

267
00:15:44,700 --> 00:15:45,540
Bai Shan.

268
00:15:46,410 --> 00:15:47,250
Bai Shan.

269
00:16:02,650 --> 00:16:03,490
Xiao Yan.

270
00:16:07,900 --> 00:16:09,090
Protect our academy.

271
00:16:27,650 --> 00:16:28,490
Bai Shan!

272
00:16:33,350 --> 00:16:34,210
Bai Shan.

273
00:16:34,260 --> 00:16:35,100
Xun'er...

274
00:16:37,380 --> 00:16:38,220
What?

275
00:16:46,140 --> 00:16:46,980
Take me

276
00:16:49,460 --> 00:16:50,300
back to the Academy.

277
00:16:52,700 --> 00:16:53,540
Take me back.

278
00:16:54,970 --> 00:16:55,810
I will.

279
00:16:56,290 --> 00:16:57,130
Let's get back.

280
00:16:59,380 --> 00:17:00,220
Bai Shan!

281
00:17:06,770 --> 00:17:07,610
Headmaster.

282
00:17:08,890 --> 00:17:09,730
Elder Hao.

283
00:17:16,460 --> 00:17:20,290
Bai Shan gave this to us before he died.

284
00:17:20,820 --> 00:17:22,220
For his brother.

285
00:17:38,110 --> 00:17:38,980
Boy,

286
00:17:39,260 --> 00:17:40,700
it was so silly of you.

287
00:17:41,580 --> 00:17:44,980
How could I explain to your brother?

288
00:17:47,300 --> 00:17:48,860
He made some mistakes before.

289
00:17:50,380 --> 00:17:51,220
But in Feng City,

290
00:17:52,340 --> 00:17:53,900
he sacrificed himself to protect us.

291
00:17:57,660 --> 00:17:59,180
He owes nothing to Jia Nan Academy.

292
00:18:01,580 --> 00:18:03,020
Nobody is perfect.

293
00:18:04,060 --> 00:18:05,340
Everyone makes mistakes.

294
00:18:07,060 --> 00:18:08,420
It was brave of him

295
00:18:09,820 --> 00:18:11,140
to fix his mistakes.

296
00:18:38,700 --> 00:18:39,540
You know what?

297
00:18:41,940 --> 00:18:45,340
Bai Shan used to say
he wanted to rank first

298
00:18:47,340 --> 00:18:49,940
and be one of a kind at Jia Nan Academy.

299
00:18:53,540 --> 00:18:54,820
Does the ranking

300
00:18:55,740 --> 00:18:56,980
really matter that much to him?

301
00:19:00,700 --> 00:19:02,580
To many of us,

302
00:19:04,180 --> 00:19:06,100
