304
00:19:11,460 --> 00:19:13,860
To Bai Shan, it means more.

305
00:19:17,860 --> 00:19:20,140
His brother Bai Cheng ranks third.

306
00:19:22,780 --> 00:19:24,900
Bai Shan always wanted

307
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:27,100
to overmatch his brother.

308
00:19:30,220 --> 00:19:32,260
Then, when people talked about him,

309
00:19:34,140 --> 00:19:36,020
