Bai Cheng's little brother.

310
00:19:39,780 --> 00:19:42,940
Maybe his brother
only wanted him to be safe.

311
00:19:45,900 --> 00:19:46,740
What did you say?

312
00:19:49,620 --> 00:19:50,460
I said,

313
00:19:52,100 --> 00:19:52,980
Bai Shan's brother

314
00:19:53,980 --> 00:19:55,420
would be proud

315
00:19:55,420 --> 00:19:56,340
of having him.

316
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:21,260
Has Black Submerged Army
got everything ready

317
00:20:21,260 --> 00:20:22,340
in the Blackhorn Domain?

318
00:20:24,140 --> 00:20:25,580
Since Han Feng escaped,

319
00:20:25,980 --> 00:20:27,140
that domain has been unpopulated.

320
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:28,100
It's very quiet.

321
00:20:28,380 --> 00:20:29,340
You can stay there

322
00:20:29,340 --> 00:20:30,540
for some days

323
00:20:30,540 --> 00:20:31,500
before you decide what to do.

324
00:20:32,500 --> 00:20:33,860
Thank you for this, Xun'er.

325
00:20:35,340 --> 00:20:36,180
But,

326
00:20:36,820 --> 00:20:37,740
I'm still worried.

327
00:20:40,140 --> 00:20:41,940
About Xiao Yan?

328
00:20:44,380 --> 00:20:45,860
His clan has been in such big trouble.

329
00:20:46,620 --> 00:20:47,460
He must be simmering

330
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:49,500
to fight Yun Shan.

331
00:20:50,940 --> 00:20:52,060
I fear he may be too impatient

332
00:20:52,740 --> 00:20:53,580
and fall into some traps.

333
00:20:54,940 --> 00:20:55,780
But anyway,

334
00:20:56,260 --> 00:20:57,340
as long as you're by his side,

335
00:20:58,460 --> 00:21:00,300
when he fights someone and thinks of you,

336
00:21:01,180 --> 00:21:02,020
he will know

337
00:21:02,620 --> 00:21:03,500
that he can't die.

338
00:21:07,820 --> 00:21:09,540
I know what you mean.

339
00:21:10,100 --> 00:21:12,580
Don't worry.
I'll always be there for Xiao Yan.

340
00:21:14,460 --> 00:21:15,940
Start your journey without concern.

341
00:21:32,620 --> 00:21:33,460
Xiao Yan has conquered

342
00:21:33,700 --> 00:21:34,740
the Fallen Heart Flame.

343
00:21:36,820 --> 00:21:38,500
The problem of the Xiao Clan is over, too.

344
00:21:39,100 --> 00:21:40,260
What are you going to do?

345
00:21:42,620 --> 00:21:44,580
We don't know
if Xiao Yan's father is still alive.

346
00:21:44,860 --> 00:21:46,660
How can that be over?

347
00:21:48,500 --> 00:21:49,340
Are you saying

348
00:21:49,980 --> 00:21:51,700
you'll go with Xiao Yan
to save his father?

349
00:21:54,300 --> 00:21:55,740
I grew up in his family.

350
00:21:56,260 --> 00:21:58,220
His father treated me as his daughter.

351
00:21:58,820 --> 00:22:00,660
Before I see he's safe,

352
00:22:00,860 --> 00:22:02,140
I will not be relieved.

353
00:22:03,700 --> 00:22:04,980
I wrote back

354
00:22:05,780 --> 00:22:06,940
about what happened here.

355
00:22:07,460 --> 00:22:08,460
The patriarch ordered me

356
00:22:09,420 --> 00:22:10,620
to take you back

357
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:12,220
within this month.

358
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:14,580
I can't help with this.

359
00:22:14,860 --> 00:22:16,020
Why did you do that?

360
00:22:19,820 --> 00:22:20,660
Xun'er,

361
00:22:21,980 --> 00:22:23,960
you've been away from our clan
for a dozen years.

362
00:22:24,780 --> 00:22:25,660
Have you thought

363
00:22:26,580 --> 00:22:28,580
about how the patriarch
spent all these years?

364
00:22:41,100 --> 00:22:41,940
