365
00:22:44,140 --> 00:22:45,980
When the problem
of the Xiao Clan is over,

366
00:22:47,620 --> 00:22:48,820
I will go back with you.

367
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:00,580
Mr. Yao,

368
