assume the worst about people?

393
00:26:46,940 --> 00:26:47,820
Oh, I see.

394
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:50,780
Because I took your Dou Qi, huh?

395
00:26:52,220 --> 00:26:54,420
You're still vindictive and you hate me.

396
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:55,280
Why do I have

397
00:26:55,290 --> 00:26:57,060
such a narrow-minded disciple?

398
00:27:04,940 --> 00:27:05,780
Greetings, Master.

399
00:27:06,060 --> 00:27:07,500
I'm your disciple from now on.

400
00:27:12,180 --> 00:27:13,060
All right, then.

401
00:27:13,580 --> 00:27:15,060
Get up. Come on.

402
00:27:21,660 --> 00:27:22,500
Master,

403
00:27:22,740 --> 00:27:25,220
when the Bone Spirit Cold Flame came out,

404
00:27:26,140 --> 00:27:27,820
