- Stop it.

405
00:27:28,140 --> 00:27:29,140
Practice hard

406
00:27:29,500 --> 00:27:31,060
and show me what you can do.

407
00:27:31,660 --> 00:27:34,340
You won't deserve
the Bone Spirit Cold Flame until then.

408
00:27:40,580 --> 00:27:41,900
Han Feng, darn it.

409
00:27:42,900 --> 00:27:43,980
He tried to kill you so many times.

410
00:27:44,740 --> 00:27:46,860
Once I see him again, I won't let him go!

411
00:27:49,900 --> 00:27:51,260
Han Feng is hateful,

412
00:27:52,780 --> 00:27:55,180
but he's a mere minion.

413
00:27:55,860 --> 00:27:57,020
The Hall of Souls

414
00:27:57,300 --> 00:27:59,260
that triggered his greediness

415
00:27:59,820 --> 00:28:01,800
and instigated him to kill his master
is the worst enemy.

416
00:28:01,860 --> 00:28:02,780
The Hall of Souls?

417
00:28:05,020 --> 00:28:07,700
It was an evil organization
raging across the Central Plains.

418
00:28:09,020 --> 00:28:11,340
They did anything to get power.

419
00:28:13,020 --> 00:28:15,740
They horribly sucked Dou Qi
from Dou Practitioners

420
00:28:15,820 --> 00:28:17,100
and it lasted a thousand years.

421
00:28:19,180 --> 00:28:20,140
Fifty years ago,

422
00:28:20,940 --> 00:28:23,540
their new leader Hun Miesheng emerged.

423
00:28:24,980 --> 00:28:27,740
I led my sect to fight them alone
in the Central Plains.

424
00:28:28,060 --> 00:28:29,420
When we were about to win,

425
00:28:30,740 --> 00:28:33,500
Elder Mu Gu of the Hall of Souls
bribed Han Feng

426
00:28:34,580 --> 00:28:35,900
to kill me unexpectedly.

427
00:28:37,460 --> 00:28:38,300
Mu Gu?

428
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:43,140
Well,

429
00:28:43,420 --> 00:28:44,780
he used to be my junior.

430
00:28:46,220 --> 00:28:47,060
But in the end,

431
00:28:47,780 --> 00:28:49,980
he was seduced
by Hun Miesheng's evil power

432
00:28:50,500 --> 00:28:51,420
and joined the Hall of Souls.

433
00:28:53,900 --> 00:28:54,980
Later, my disciple

434
00:28:55,860 --> 00:28:57,220
worked for them, too.

435
00:29:02,380 --> 00:29:04,260
Compared to wicked techniques,

436
00:29:05,620 --> 00:29:07,340
